OL,5,G1105 Secrets of the Royal Palaces
OL,6,     FHow, in 1698, Nottingham House was
OL,7,     Fbought and renovated by William
OL,8,     FIII, turning it into Kensington
OL,9,     FPalace. Plus; the event where
OL,10,     FPrincess Diana wore her famous
OL,11,     F'revenge' dress.
OL,12,G1205 Blenheim Palace: Behind the
OL,13,G     Grandeur
OL,14,     FThe events team have a busy
OL,15,     Fweekend as the Knights of Middle
OL,16,     FEngland perform at a jousting
OL,17,     Fevent. Kate is excited to receive
OL,18,     Fsome paintings by Winston
OL,19,     FChurchill. (Ep3/4)
